sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Frontend
    participant FastAPI
    participant NLP_Algorithm
    participant Database

    User->>Frontend: Fill report form (desc, photo, GPS)
    Frontend->>FastAPI: POST /report (multipart + JWT)
    FastAPI->>FastAPI: Verify JWT token
    FastAPI->>FastAPI: Save photo to /uploads
    FastAPI->>NLP_Algorithm: calculate_severity_score(description)
    NLP_Algorithm-->>FastAPI: score + label (Critical/High/Moderate/Low)
    FastAPI->>Database: INSERT Case with severity
    Database-->>FastAPI: New Case record
    FastAPI-->>Frontend: Case JSON response
    Frontend-->>User: Case reported! Severity badge shown
